reviews.review_text: this is a good aud now that ya'll got the date figured (thanks), i figured i best post up a rating.  very good.  sounds almost like a good matrix...  some VERY nice playing as well.  i went for the dl, i might suggest that yo do the same.

one of a kind The first set tunes are played with gusto and the second set is amazing. This was (to me) the best set since 9/2/78. Between this and Morning Dew in Rochester four days prior, Grateful Dead had made a significant impression.
